search for the coords of your home eg i searched “2792” and it came up with my initial starting point

// initial x and y coordinates of the player heightLevel = 0; // the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet teleportToX = 2792; // 2792; teleportToY = 3168; // 3168;
